          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Requires the President's annual budget submission to Congress to provide an estimate of the pro rata cost to individuals who file an income tax return of any projected deficit for the fiscal year.</p>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-03-24T21:37:38Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
