        <item>
          <versionCode>81</versionCode>
          <actionDesc>Passed House without amendment</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.)</b></p> <p>Requires the President's annual buget submission to Congress to provide an estimate of the pro rata cost to individuals who file an income tax return of any projected deficit for the fiscal year.</p>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2013-03-07T19:37:01Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
